Package: openvpn-server
Version: 1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Said Arabov <arabovseyitnazar@gmail.com>
Depends: ufw, openvpn
Description: Automated OpenVPN server installer with Easy-RSA support
 This package installs an automated OpenVPN server provisioning script that
 sets up a full CA using Easy-RSA, generates server/client certificates, configures
 the server, updates firewall (UFW), and generates ready-to-use client .ovpn files.
 Designed for easy deployment of secure VPN infrastructure.
